milestones.description: Ryan ten Doeschate has become the top scorer for NED in ODIs with 605 runs, going past Bas Zuiderent's 594
Romaine has broken the record for most ducks (4) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Clay Smith's 3
Tom de Grooth and Kervezee's 154-run partnership is NED's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 114 between Bas Zuiderent and Reekers
Leverock has become the top wicket-taker for BMUDA in ODIs with 24 wickets, going past Mukuddem's 23
This is the highest match aggregate (458) involving teams Bermuda & Netherlands in ODIs
Netherlands's 173-run win against Bermuda is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 117-run win against Canada

stories.subTitle: Netherlands v Bermuda, 1st ODI, Rotterdam
stories.summary: Half-centuries by openers Tom de Grooth, Alexei Kervezee and a late flourish from Mudassar Bukhari set up Netherlands' 172-run win against Bermuda in the first ODI at Rotterdam
